{"tid":2308671,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「西螺羅志祥」被騙吞威而鋼 遭138公斤乩童強迫口爆崩潰提告","createTime":"2020-12-02T05:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T11:58:23.000Z","uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"bd54fa16cd56ea203e9d3c7b6cedbfed37a73080","tid":2308671,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"雲林一名宮廟乩童因為對信眾有好感，前年稱對方遭警察跟蹤，要求對方到宮廟住一陣子<br />\n，趁兩人獨處時，將威而鋼騙稱是調養藥物，等對方吃下說「身體發熱就要脫衣服」，接<br />\n著以重達138公斤的身體重壓、為其口交。該信眾因外表出眾，有「西螺羅志祥」稱號，<br />\n事發後提告，一審判4年徒刑，經上訴後法院駁回，維持原判決。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n判決書指出，該信眾因為買賣車輛糾紛纏訟多年，經常與哥哥、母親到該宮廟求籤問卦，<br />\n該乩童因此對他心生好感，甚至對他說「你身體出問題」、「生殖器不會勃起」等言論，<br />\n企圖以神職人員身分博取相信。該乩童前年5月先是打電話向對方哥哥說，對方目前被警<br />\n察跟蹤，要對方當晚帶著衣物來宮殿住幾天，可以保護其安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201202002107-260402?chdtv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20201202002107-260402%3Fchdtv&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2Wmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=64baf72f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201202002107-260402?chdtv</a>"},{"pid":"ec51dbd26cccd14f252b72af714fce46674f8986","tid":2308671,"uid":73269,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:33:00.000Z","msg":"乩童？？"},{"pid":"3bbb5aed9fbf5bbbdf5f60ff4d343877f79a2f7f","tid":2308671,"uid":60977,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:38:10.000Z","msg":"杰哥不要啊"},{"pid":"7b1ec17dfc510aff0d1f8fc3042aefbc23260f4d","tid":2308671,"uid":83328,"like":39,"dislike":4,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"ec51dbd26cccd14f252b72af714fce46674f8986","tid":2308671,"uid":73269,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:33:00.000Z","msg":"乩童？？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:39:18.000Z","msg":"所以點解叫羅志祥<br />\n<img src=\"https://cache.hkgolden.media/compress/https://media.giphy.com/media/bCinKazVtGEy4/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A